{"id": 747, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对知乎的使用体验有什么不满？", "description": "也是看够了个人奋斗史和骗图钓鱼帖。", "record_count": 6260, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183714w0A5i4DGTLqtBIp1.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-17T11:02:12Z", "options": [{"id": 50944, "content": "更新比较慢", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475479}, {"id": 51456, "content": "答完问题就各种推荐微信公众号，比传销高逼格了一点点", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480476}, {"id": 50945, "content": "做过实验，认真回答专业问题，被评论不懂别瞎bb。吹牛装逼时，被评论大神请收下膝盖！", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459920}, {"id": 50946, "content": "不用知乎，查资料出现链接会进去看。\n满屏的数据，阅读体验并不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476671}, {"id": 51202, "content": "楼主提的这个问题啊，exciting！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462619}, {"id": 50947, "content": "一定要提的搜索功能！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476701}, {"id": 50948, "content": "专业问题大V说了句吐槽的话也能被顶到首位", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476701}, {"id": 50951, "content": "我提的问题，没有人回答！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258958}, {"id": 50952, "content": "g j j j", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476728}, {"id": 51466, "content": "我想知道之前的知乎是什么样子的，表好奇", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480015}, {"id": 50956, "content": "伪科学", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235574}, {"id": 50958, "content": "网页版看着就不舒服，字太小，背景太白。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476773}, {"id": 50964, "content": "必须是搜索功能烂成屎。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305652}, {"id": 56852, "content": "谁是知乎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507235}, {"id": 50965, "content": "开篇的前几段写了一堆答后感和“高深”的影子\n读下去的欲望都没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 457467}, {"id": 50966, "content": "越来越无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 50967, "content": "有些答案字太多 又不写结论 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475710}, {"id": 50968, "content": "并没有什么感受", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454454}, {"id": 50970, "content": "好装逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380121}, {"id": 51227, "content": "我觉得知乎上好多深奥的问题我都遇不到，以前看微博觉得知乎上的问的问题真好，但下完知乎以后，心情瞬间就变了，有些完全看不懂。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468554}, {"id": 50974, "content": "好多话好多好多话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461133}, {"id": 50976, "content": "知乎的搜索并不好用", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168123}, {"id": 50980, "content": "永远不停的争论！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 474074}, {"id": 51237, "content": "知道多了，就身陷其中……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478925}, {"id": 50983, "content": "女权癌太多……而且有些特别恐怖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198124}, {"id": 50984, "content": "感觉无限制消耗精力，什么都想知道，然而并没有太大作用，还是回归现实好好工作，生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171964}, {"id": 51752, "content": "知乎不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277188}, {"id": 50985, "content": "大V效应……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 317776}, {"id": 50986, "content": "少了干货", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228456}, {"id": 51242, "content": "我玩知乎发现有好奇心日报广告。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 50578}, {"id": 52267, "content": "从知乎日报不太行到重新做了一个读读日报并经常在知乎日报推读读日报，其实我觉得知乎日报不错了，虽然里面分类的内容也是蛮糟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484251}, {"id": 50988, "content": "起初作为专业人士的社区由于开放注册，用于一大批不怎么专业的用户，导致出现众多不经过大脑的回答和喷子们的评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 378585}, {"id": 50989, "content": "testing", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004757N1jPB7pzueyElUMH.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476897}, {"id": 51245, "content": "把错误的理论说的好有根据的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478959}, {"id": 51246, "content": "知乎会不会写\n你对好奇心日报有何不满", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235289}, {"id": 51247, "content": "主页如果能像果壳网一样好就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 421150}, {"id": 50992, "content": "你對好奇心日报有什么不满︶︿︶", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 329595}, {"id": 50993, "content": "无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431137}, {"id": 50994, "content": "慢慢地向贴吧，微博看齐了", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 387218}, {"id": 50995, "content": "你们的戾气很重阿", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 339897}, {"id": 51251, "content": "慢慢的变成了百度知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128066}, {"id": 50996, "content": "少问点：如何评价……式问题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464170}, {"id": 63540, "content": "尼玛有的看不懂 觉得自己好傻逼┐（─__─）┌", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546877}, {"id": 50997, "content": "滋生民粹而不自知的土壤。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272505}, {"id": 50998, "content": "认真回答一个问题，却没人给我点赞（忧桑脸）", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476982}, {"id": 50999, "content": "穆黑聚集地?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 203582}, {"id": 51001, "content": "知乎豆瓣化，豆瓣贴吧化，贴吧FB化…", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476997}, {"id": 51002, "content": "13年惊为天人，16年沦为路人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453445}, {"id": 52282, "content": "找不到自己曾经发的评论与答案", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484369}, {"id": 51003, "content": "还行，我看行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476979}]}